<br>
I read the chart on the fist damage and delay and have a question.<br>
<br>
I am using 2 polished steel ulaks given to me by someone (which was real cool) they do <br>
9 damage to 27 delay for a ratio of 3  (27/9=3) and looking at the fist chart it looks like my fist will not do better, ratio wise until about level 35 when I have 11 damage at a 33 delay for a ratio of 3 (33/11=3). Based on that it seems like the PSU are better until then. Am I missing something on this or is this a correct assumption.<br>
<br>
Any help in this matter is greatly appreciated.<br>
Thanks<br>
<br>
Lthiny <br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/uandsonquietfist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Andson Quietfist</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 31<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(5/24/02 10:17:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1537.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://ourworld.cs.com/harshbind/SilverFlame/images/Andson1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PSU or Hands Until when?</span><hr size=1> Yup, looks right to me. Someone's going to mention the damage bonus thing, so I'll go ahead. When you hit 28, you'll get a damage bonus. Not sure if that applies to the PSU's or not (I think it does), but it does apply to your fist. At level 28 when you get the damage bonus, you want a good ratio AND a low delay in your primary hand, so I would still stick with the Ulaks, as their delay is lower so your damage bonus would get applied more often. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=83770">Andson Funkymunky</a><BR>
