<br>
I was still using one at 44 (yes, I know...) simply because of the stat bonuses.  I procrastinated about banking it because I didn't want to lose the bonuses it gave me.  However, I'm glad I did now because my damage with my fist is much, much better.<br>
<br>
Get some nice HP items sorted before you ditch them, otherwise you'll be tempted to keep using 'em...!<br>
